o transcending the cycle of karma.", "verse_ranges": ["gopa_1.1.15", "gopa_1.1.30"]}, {"teaching": "The story of Maudgalya and Maitreya illustrates that true knowledge is not mere recitation but understanding the essence (Om).", "lens_note": "Sharma would interpret this as the difference between intellectual learning and experiential realization through Kriya.", "verse_ranges": ["gopa_1.1.31", "gopa_1.1.32"]}], "_provenance": {"purana": "Gopatha Brahmana", "chapter_label": "Chapter 0 (part 2)", "seq_start": 81, "seq_end": 160, "chunk_ids": ["gopatha-0-81", "gopatha-0-82", "gopatha-0-83", "gopatha-0-84", "gopatha-0-85", "gopatha-0-86", "gopatha-0-87", "gopatha-0-88", "gopatha-0-89", "gopatha-0-90", "gopatha-0-91", "gopatha-0-92", "gopatha-0-93", "gopatha-0-94", "gopatha-0-95", "gopatha-0-96", "gopatha-0-97", "gopatha-0-98", "gopatha-0-99", "gopatha-0-100", "gopatha-0-101", "gopatha-0-102", "gopatha-0-103", "gopatha-0-104", "gopatha-0-105", "gopatha-0-106", "gopatha-0-107", "gopatha-0-108", "gopatha-0-109", "gopatha-0-110", "gopatha-0-111", "gopatha-0-112", "gopatha-0-113", "gopatha-0-114", "gopatha-0-115", "gopatha-0-116", "gopatha-0-117", "gopatha-0-118", "gopatha-0-119", "gopatha-0-120", "gopatha-0-121", "gopatha-0-122", "gopatha-0-123", "gopatha-0-124", "gopatha-0-125", "gopatha-0-126", "gopatha-0-127", "gopatha-0-128", "gopatha-0-129", "gopatha-0-130", "gopatha-0-131", "gopatha-0-132", "gopatha-0-133", "gopatha-0-134", "gopatha-0-135", "gopatha-0-136", "gopatha-0-137", "gopatha-0-138", "gopatha-0-139", "gopatha-0-140", "gopatha-0-141", "gopatha-0-142", "gopatha-0-143", "gopatha-0-144", "gopatha-0-145", "gopatha-0-146", "gopatha-0-147", "gopatha-0-148", "gopatha-0-149", "gopatha-0-150", "gopatha-0-151", "gopatha-0-152", "gopatha-0-153", "gopatha-0-154", "gopatha-0-155", "gopatha-0-156", "gopatha-0-157", "gopatha-0-158", "gopatha-0-159", "gopatha-0-160"], "provider": "deepseek", "model": "deepseek-chat", "lens_applied": true, "salvaged": false, "pruned_invalid_node